---
const PRODUCT_IMG = 'https://bswmrfxdadcmuyhmsagv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/portfolio-images/test.jpeg';
---
<section class="artist">
  <div class="artist__inner">
    <div class="artist__img reveal">
      <img src={PRODUCT_IMG} alt="Delvin Begay — portrait" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="artist__eyebrow reveal">◆ Artist Spotlight · No. 12</div>
      <h2 class="artist__title reveal reveal--d1">Delvin <em>Begay</em></h2>
      <p class="artist__quote reveal reveal--d2">
        "Every stone has already decided what it wants to be. My job is just to listen and not mess it up."
      </p>
      <p class="artist__body reveal reveal--d2">
        Third-generation Navajo silversmith working out of a corrugated-tin shop outside
        Window Rock. Delvin's clusters are what put the "tacky" in Tacky Turquoise — loud,
        heavy, unapologetic, and completely unrepeatable.
      </p>
      <div class="artist__stats reveal reveal--d3">
        <div class="artist__stat"><div class="num">19</div><div class="lbl">Years silversmithing</div></div>
        <div class="artist__stat"><div class="num">42</div><div class="lbl">Pieces in this drop</div></div>
        <div class="artist__stat"><div class="num">1 of 1</div><div class="lbl">Every single time</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
